name: Jones Canyon
description:
Introduction

Jones Canyon comes off of Jones Peak, East of Bailey Canyon and Hiker Bob Canyon. The initial drop in is pretty thick with brush but eventually lets up lower in the canyon. A handful of good rappels and some nice views into the Valley gives this canyon a bit of redemption after the initial hike and bushwhack.
